Governor Yahaya Bello of Kogi state on Saturday swept his polling unit for President Muhammadu Buhari and the National Assembly candidates of the All Progressives Congress (APC) in the state. Here are the results below: Presidential APC – 407 PDP- 0 INVALID-1  Senate APC-_405 PDP-0 SDP-0 INVALID-3  House of Reps APC- 403 PDP-0 SDP-0 Invalid-5. Kogi Supplementary Election: Bello in early lead APC, PDP test strength in Buhari’s base tomorrow We will defend mandate of Kogi people – Faleke